TheDessertHouse is a CMS app built using ASP.NET MVC 3. The Views are created with the Razor engine. It uses NHibernate 3 as the ORM framework and StructureMap 2.6.2 for DI.
The DB is Sql Server 2008 R2
ORM Persistence test are run against SqlList DB. All other Unit tests use the Open source MVCContrib project where interacting with ASP.NET components is involved
Client side code is written in JQuery and uses JQuery templates extensively

Conceptually the app is similar to TheBeerHouseApp 